    <a href="#" style=" text-decoration: none; color: #000000;">Community</a>
    <a href="#" style=" text-decoration: none; color: #000000;">Jobs</a>
    <a href="#" style=" text-decoration: none; color: #000000;">Privacy and Policy</a>
    <a href="#" style=" text-decoration: none; color: #000000;">More</a>
</div>
